    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "NEW YORK, July 6—(AP)—Certain laws of human eye-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "sight will explain much of what has been described about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "the flying saucers reported from nearly all parts of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "United States.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "At any distance which is close",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "to the limit of how far a person",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "can see, all objects appear round",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "or nearly so. This law of sight",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "covers both small things seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "nearby and large ones at great",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "distances.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Regardless of shape, the ob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "ject near the limit of sight looks",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "round. If the thing is silhouetted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "against a bright sky, as some of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "the flying saucers have been re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "ported, then it is more likely to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "reveal its true shape.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "HAVE 'NO STRUCTURE'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "If the thing is seen by reflected",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "light, as in most cases reported,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "it is almost certain to be round,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "and if the reflections are sunlight,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "then the sizes reported are those",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "which would be expected from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "distant light reflections.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "The one outstanding fact about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "virtually all the saucers is that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "they had no structure — they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "seemed merely round and flat.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "That description fits exactly with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "the tricks that eyes play. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "trickiness varies with differences",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "in weather and lighting.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "This writer has seen flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "saucers over Long Island Sound",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "near his home, not only this year",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "but in previous years. They were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "round, bright and moving fast.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "NOT A MYSTERY",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "But they were no mystery be-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "cause they were light reflected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "from the bodies of airplanes that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "soon identified themselves by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "changing course and coming near",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "enough to be seen distinctly.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "Last week this writer also saw",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "one oval flying form which for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "a moment looked exactly like the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "photograph of the oval object",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "taken by Yeoman Frank Ryman",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "north of Seattle, Wash. The Long",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "Island oval came closer and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
