      "text": "turned into an airplane.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "Planes at great distances tend",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "to look round when light is re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "flected from their sides. Many",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "descriptions of movements of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "flying saucers fit with the com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "mon maneuvers of airplanes,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "singly or in groups.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "They fit also with what birds",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "look like, flying at a considerable",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "distance. However the bird illu-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "sion is not very common. Some",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "of the maneuvering reported,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "which took saucers out of sight",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "and back into sight again re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
